WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:02.000
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON
GHOST WHISPERER...</i>

00:03.400 --> 00:06.000
Melinda: THERE'S A DOOR IN THE
ARCHIVES THAT LEADS TO THE TUNNELS.

00:07.700 --> 00:09.600
WAIT A MINUTE,
ARE YOU SAYING

00:09.600 --> 00:10.900
WHAT I THINK YOU'RE SAYING?

00:12.100 --> 00:13.500
LET'S HAVE A BABY.

00:14.300 --> 00:16.500
OH! OH, GOD,
I LOVE YOU.

00:17.800 --> 00:18.500
Melinda: WHAT?

00:18.500 --> 00:19.900
THAT'S WEIRD.

00:20.700 --> 00:24.900
THERE'S SIX OF US, BUT
THERE'S ONLY FIVE SHADOWS.

